# oVirt 4.3-only: 4.4 dropped the separate Image I/O Proxy
# (ovirt-imageio-proxy) setup question, so the 4.4 answers we copied from
# omit it and 4.3's engine-setup hangs on it ("End of file"). Answer yes so
# the engine can proxy disk uploads (exercised by the smoke test).
